I went to Japan for two weeks, and this was day 2 in Tokyo!!

We spent most of the day in Shibuya, starting at Shibuya Scramble Square, stopping by RURU SHIBUYA for floating matcha, and taking in the views at Shibuya Sky.

Of course we had to see Shibuya Crossing, then ended the night with dinner at Han no Daidokoro.

Follow along for day 3 in Harajuku!
